column.Name: ComponentType

column.Name: ComponentSizeHeaderName
column.lookupquery: SELECT ItemKey, ItemValue FROM dvtComponentSizeHeaderName WHERE Active = 1 ORDER BY ItemSort, ItemValue

column.Name: Active
